						<summary>

						

						<p>Registers the grant of land to Appalāchārya in the <hi rend="bold">Rāmānujakūṭa</hi> of Kadiri-sthaḷa by <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Sundara Abiḷarājaya. Also provision was made for providing food-offerings to the god Nārasiṁha and the Āḷvārs.</p>						

